<lyrics>[V1]
 kào zhe dǎo gào kè fú kùn nán, miè jǐn è zhě yī qiè huǒ jiàn,
 xiàng yǐ lì shā chū dào shuǐ yuán, bǎ yán dào zài shuǐ lǐ biān.
 chū dào shuǐ yuán chū dào shuǐ yuán, bǎ yán dào zài shuǐ lǐ biān.
 gāo shān píng yuán sāi wài jiāng nán, chù chù dōu shì guǒ mǎn yuán.
 nǐ yào qǐ lái nǐ yào zhēng zhàn, bǎ yán dào zài shuǐ lǐ biān.
 zhǔ gěi zhōng guó zhù fú mǎn mǎn nǐ yào qǐ lái kuài zhēng zhàn.</lyrics>
<title>chū dào shuǐ yuán 迦南554</title>
